## Image Guidelines

- **Format**: PNG for screenshots, JPG for photos, SVG for icons
- **Size**: Optimize for web (under 500KB per image)
- **Resolution**: High-DPI ready (2x resolution recommended)
- **Alt Text**: All images should have descriptive alt text in markdown
- **Consistency**: Use consistent styling and branding across all images

## Adding Images

1. Add image files to this directory
2. Reference them in markdown files using relative paths
3. Always include descriptive alt text for accessibility
4. Test images display correctly in both light and dark themes

Example usage in markdown:
```markdown
![My Attend Dashboard](images/screenshot-dashboard.png)
```